Record Group 17. Digital formats (1989-2013, undated; 4.5 linear feet)

This series consists of the physical CDs, DVDs, 3.5 inch floppy disks, and other digital media in the collection that have been processed, and the digital files that have been retrieved and preserved from most of that media. Digital files were not retrieved from damaged, duplicate, and commercially available CDs or due to disk formatting issues. Subseries I.A includes the digital files which may be requested and accessed. Subseries I.B refers to the media and, based on the labeling, provides a sense of the scope and content of the digital files.
